Sentencas: The microstructure of anode has a significant influence on the whole electrochemical performance of solid oxide direct carbon fuel cells (SO-DCFCs).
Titulo: Influence of anode's microstructure on electrochemical performance of solid oxide direct carbon fuel cells

Sentencas: The tubular SO-DCFCs based on cathode supported solid oxide fuel cells was fabricated by dip-coating and co-sintering techniques.
Titulo: Influence of anode's microstructure on electrochemical performance of solid oxide direct carbon fuel cells

Sentencas: As the anode porosity mainly came from the pore former (graphite) in the dip-coating process, different contents of graphite were added into the anode slurries.
Titulo: Influence of anode's microstructure on electrochemical performance of solid oxide direct carbon fuel cells

Sentencas: When the graphite was 10.1% wt., the SO-DCFCs showed the best performance and stability.
Titulo: Influence of anode's microstructure on electrochemical performance of solid oxide direct carbon fuel cells

Sentencas: The peak power density reached 242 mW cm(-2) at 850 degrees C, with carbon black (located 5% Fe) as the fuel and air as the oxidant.
